			<div id="academics_left" style="overflow:hidden;color:#660000;height:100%;"><!---Start of academics left side--->
				<span style="color:#660000;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;">
				Placement Procedure:</span><br><br>
				<ul type="i">
					<li>The Training and Placement Officer, UIIT, sends an invitation to companies/ organizations 
					with relevant information.</li>
					<li>The company/organization is required to send their response/confirmation via email.</li>
					<li>The placement incharge will allot dates for the campus interviews as per information provided
					through the e-mail. The company/organization can confirm or negotiate the dates with the
					placement incharge.</li>
					<li>The requisite information is mailed to the company/organization. The company/organization is 
					required to furnish the final list of students as soon as possible after the completion of the 
					selection procedure.</li>
				</ul>
				<p>Feel free to contact Training and Placement Cell, UIIT Shimla.<br>
					<a href="/contact_us" style="text-decoration:none;color:#1e90ff;font-size:15px;
						font-weight:bold;float:right;">Contact Us</a>

